schools.name: Clifford O. Pete Findlay Middle School

data.description: Located in a Gated Community near Tule Springs, this 4-bedroom, 2.5-bath residence exudes charm, complete with an added loft! Tiled throughout the ground level, amplifying its charm. With its uniquely crafted stone accent wall, the family room stands out! The primary bathroom features stylish sinks, meanwhile, the kitchen stands out as a haven for chefs, featuring a custom island, granite countertops, a chic backsplash, and a built-in microwave. The home's appeal is further accentuated by its backyard, complete with synthetic grass, a serene spa, and a shaded patio.
